token_lists.title: NEO Crew (loures1987)
token_lists.description:
- Did you really have to blow up the whole lab, Nyselmorth? Is that what "keeping a low profile" means to you? - asked Romeo. His eyes were now red due to all vessels in his sclera tearing down due to the explosion.
- What could be more quiet and low than a place where everybody is dead? - answered Nyselmorth, giving a mad laugh that made the whole crew chill. It didn't matter how long the crew was together, they never got used to her.
- Stop talking and walk faster! This cryo is not going to get himself on the ship. - said Conquitus. 

The three kept walking the fast they could while carrying a cryo coffin, with the payload inside.
 
In the meantime Koruy went scouting in the front to ensure they wouldn't be facing any surprises. 
- Ciel, we have just passed by Echo Uno. All clear up to now. ETA for rendez-vous in 1 click. Gears on baby.
- Copy that, Koruy. Have you certified you don't have any heat at your 6? 
- Only ghosts. After Nyse went all Nyse in there, I would really doubt anyone has their heads attached to their heads still.
-  Damn that lunatic. Did she say again that it was the bird that told her to do it?
- ...Yes...
- Oh great. Tonight I'm giving that Gogo to Conquitus Omni. But nevermind, engines are on. In a few moments we get it over with and receive our fortune of 1 whole Tezo. I'll be buying myself an exoplanet with my part and.... 
*BOOM!* 
A noise so loud was made that Ciel managed to hear it from the ship, now 300 meters away.
- What was that? Did anyone die?
- ....
- Koruy, are you still there?
-...

A moment of dispar went through Ciels head. But just before she could do any conjectures, an answer came through.
- Capitan, Nyse just blew up the head of the payload. - said Koruy with a monotone voice as if he already expected something like this to happen. - She said she was getting tired of carrying all that weight. Gues our client will have to wait a bit more. Again...

-

token_lists.title: Valkyr Vessel - HOPPER#01 - Exploration and research of asteroid belt's flora.
token_lists.description:
Connor - androgynous party-being. Has been working as realter in the colony but is fed up with that life. Wants to go on an adventure and hired on to a knew and unknown valkyr research vessel to go an explore new frontiers on the planet. First job: see that everybody on board gets enough nutrition.

Crabby - scientist who’s ancestors lived on the planet of the apes. Has been working in mobile lab tents on foreign terrain as long as he can remember. Often grumpy. Now especiellay since two of his new crew mates are blind.

Cleiturn - seer and healer. One might wonder coming across a being like her on a research vessel but the crew has often been hurt badly exploring unknown terrain. Physically and mentally. She knows how to get her people through.

Jones - blind pathfinder. He lost his eyesight at age 11 playing with super high voltage. Usually he is to find on all four deep inside the undergrowth of strange forests. He knows all plants and animals there are to know in all the multiverse. His sensual, hearing and olfactorial abilities exceed everything you can imagine. For basic visual things his little monster assists him.

Whal - badass pilot and navigator. Wanna get out of of a collapsing asteroid rift. Hire her!

Mission -  
explore an uncharted asteroid belt. Observations suggest that the belt is rotating so fast, that artificial gravity formed facing inward to the belts center. Some bigger asteroids are supposed to have formed an atmosphere and it is likely that plants are growing there. The crews mission is to find out if that’s true. Set down on the biggest asteroid and collect samples.

token_lists.description:
The Heartbreaker is the ship that you see when everything is going fine. But then you see it... out near the periphery. The Heartbreaker's crew shows up to let you know things aren't going as well as you thought.

Mathews - This bear can fly any bird that doesn't have a heartbeat. Dedicated retro gamer.

Belytia - Information and weapons systems are her turf. Cold and competitive.

Dorsey - Captain of the Heartbreaker. Forgiving to friends. Relentless to enemies.

Stephenson - Can fly or ride anything with a heartbeat. Brash, but good natured.

Bonilla - Empath. Can influence the emotions of others. Optimistic pessimist.
